 on who decides about agricultural technology adoption.
 Here, we go one step further and look at actual adoption of the practices
 and technologies recommended in the video at the individual level.
 In particular, we compare the proportion of plots between two treatments
 on which (i) the husband solely made the decision to implement the practice
 that is recommended in the video; (ii) the wife solely made the decision
 to implement the practice that is recommended in the video; and (iii) husband
 and wife indicate they jointly made the decision to implement a particular
 practice or input as recommended in the video
